text: Ramindu Nikeshala (born 16 July 1996) is a Sri Lankan cricketer. He made his Twenty20 debut for Badureliya Sports Club in the 2017–18 SLC Twenty20 Tournament on 25 February 2018. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Sri Lankan cricketers Category:Badureliya Sports Club cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
